<figure><img src="https://sistersimms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/lauren-Copy.jpg" alt="" /></figure>

<p><!-- /wp:image --></p>

<p><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>

<p>Lauren is a senior this year at UNC. She is studying Software Engineering with a minor in Criminal Justice. Currently she has 3 jobs, two of them are on campus with one being off campus. She is a Student Ambassador which means that she gives tours to prospective high school students. She is also the Student Security Agent in the Office of Information Management &amp; Technology. She is also the Information Security Intern at Platte River Power Authority in Fort Collins. In her free time she likes to get involved with the business fraternity, Delta Sigma Pi and play intramural sports.</p>

<p>She has a background in Cyber Security and a little bit of graphic design. She also has lots of experience in customer service and speaking to large groups of people. She is working on her coding skills and gaining more knowledge in graphic design. One day she hopefully aspires to work in Cyber Security. </p>

<p> </p>

